\'e2\'80\'9cLight of my eyes: he comes! unhoped-for joy!\
Has Heaven from Pylos brought my lovely boy?\
So snatch\'e2\'80\'99d from all our cares!\'e2\'80\'94Tell, hast thou known\
Thy father\'e2\'80\'99s fate, and tell me all thy own.\'e2\'80\uc0\u157 \
