And call Jove\'e2\'80\'99s vengeance on their guilty deed.\
While to the assembled council I repair:\
A stranger sent by Heaven attends me there;\
My new accepted guest I haste to find,\
Now to Peiraeus\'e2\'80\'99 honour\'e2\'80\'99d charge consign\'e2\'80\'99d.\'e2\'80\uc0\u157 \
