Of this sure auguries the gods bestow\'e2\'80\'99d,\
When first our vessel anchor\'e2\'80\'99d in your road.\'e2\'80\uc0\u157 \
\'e2\'80\'9cSucceed those omens, Heaven! (the queen rejoin\'e2\'80\'99d)\
So shall our bounties speak a grateful mind;\
And every envied happiness attend\
