Straight to the feastful palace he repair\'e2\'80\'99d,\
Familiar enter\'e2\'80\'99d, and the banquet shared;\
Beneath Eurymachus, his patron lord,\
He took his place, and plenty heap\'e2\'80\'99d the board.\
