Bred by Ulysses, nourish\'e2\'80\'99d at his board,\
But, ah! not fated long to please his lord;\
To him, his swiftness and his strength were vain;\
The voice of glory call\'e2\'80\'99d him o\'e2\'80\'99er the main.\
